{"tha-ap222:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap222:0.2":"Hatthivagga ","tha-ap222:0.3":"Papanivariyattheraapadana ","tha-ap222:1.1":"“Piyadassissa bhagavato, ","tha-ap222:1.2":"cankamam sodhitam maya; ","tha-ap222:1.3":"Nalakehi paticchannam, ","tha-ap222:1.4":"vatatapanivaranam. ","tha-ap222:2.1":"Papam vivajjanatthaya, ","tha-ap222:2.2":"kusalassupasampada; ","tha-ap222:2.3":"Kilesanam pahanaya, ","tha-ap222:2.4":"padahim satthu sasane. ","tha-ap222:3.1":"Ito ekadase kappe, ","tha-ap222:3.2":"aggidevoti vissuto; ","tha-ap222:3.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap222:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap222:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap222:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap222:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap222:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma papanivariyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap222:6.1":"Papanivariyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap222:7.1":"Hatthivaggo bavisatimo. ","tha-ap222:8.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap222:9.1":"Hatthi panadhi saccanca, ","tha-ap222:9.2":"ekasanni ca ramsiko; ","tha-ap222:9.3":"Sandhito talavantanca, ","tha-ap222:9.4":"tatha akkantasannako; ","tha-ap222:9.5":"Sappi papanivari ca, ","tha-ap222:9.6":"catuppannasa gathakati. "}